{
  "name": "getSiteAssetStats",
  "description": "Get Site Asset Details",
  "parameters": {
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
      "start": {
        "default": 0,
        "minimum": 0,
        "type": "integer"
      },
      "end": {
        "default": 0,
        "minimum": 0,
        "type": "integer"
      },
      "duration": {
        "default": "1d",
        "example": "10m",
        "type": "string",
        "description": "For historical stats and/or logs where time range is needed, you can specify the time range in a few different ways:\n  * ?start=1430000000&end=1430864000\tspecify the start / end\n  * ?end=1430864000&duration=1d\tspecify end time and duration\n  * ?duration=1d\tspecify duration, end will be now() in seconds"
      },
      "site_id": {
        "example": "000000ab-00ab-00ab-00ab-0000000000ab",
        "format": "uuid",
        "type": "string"
      }
    },
    "required": [
      "site_id"
    ]
  },
  "handler": "http",
  "request": {
    "method": "GET",
    "url": {
      "$uri": "https://api.mist.com/api/v1/sites/{site_id}/stats/assets/asset_id{?start,end,duration}"
    }
  },
  "responses": {
    "200": {
      "$encode": "markdown",
      "$block": [
        {
          "$h1": "Object"
        },
        "Asset statistics",
        "**Key properties:**",
        {
          "$ul": [
            "**battery_voltage**: battery voltage, in mV",
            "**eddystone_uid_instance**",
            "**eddystone_uid_namespace**",
            "**eddystone_url_url**",
            "**ibeacon_major**",
            "**ibeacon_minor**",
            "**ibeacon_uuid**",
            "**last_seen**: last seen timestamp",
            "**mac**: bluetooth MAC",
            "**map_id**: map where the device belongs to",
            "**name**: name / label of the device",
            "**rssizones**: only send this for individual asset stat",
            "**x**: x in pixel",
            "**y**: y in pixel",
            "**zones**: only send this for individual asset stat"
          ]
        },
        {
          "$lang": "json",
          "$code": {
            "$encode": "json",
            "$indent": true,
            "$content": {
              "$": "$.body"
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    "400": {
      "$encode": "markdown",
      "$block": [
        {
          "$h1": "Object"
        },
        {
